org.jsapar.error

Class MulticastErrorEventListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jsapar.error.MulticastErrorEventListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, ErrorEventListener

    public class MulticastErrorEventListener
extends Object
implements ErrorEventListener
    Distributes all error events to multiple ErrorEventListener instances. All registered listeners are called one by one from the same thread. If no ErrorEventListener is registered, this implementation will throw an exception upon the first error.
